examples.en: The boxers hit each other with their fists.
He clenched his fists in anger.
She pounded on the door with both fists.
I closed my fists and got ready to fight.
He started swinging at me with his fists.
He aimed his fists towards his opponent's face.
The sudden hammer of fists caught him off guard.
She flew at him, pummelling his chest with her fists.
